---

<Layout>
  <div class="w-full flex-shrink-0 flex-col lg:w-auto">
    <div class="max-w-reading mx-2 lg:mx-0">
      <h1 class="font-title mb-3 text-6xl">Hey 👋🏼, I&rsquo;m Jakob</h1>
      <p class="font-sans text-2xl">
        I&lsquo;m a co-founder of
        <a href="https://taskless.io" class="as-link">Taskless</a>, removing the
        risks associated with adopting third party services.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-3 mb-6 font-sans text-2xl">
        The messy part of building things is my happy place. Ocassionally, I
        write about
        <a
          href="https://github.com/thecodedrift/codedrift/discussions/categories/thunked?discussions_q=is%3Aopen+category%3AThunked+label%3A%22%F0%9F%93%9A+Code%22"
          class="as-link"
        >
          code
        </a>
        and the
        <a
          href="https://github.com/thecodedrift/codedrift/discussions/categories/thunked?discussions_q=is%3Aopen+category%3AThunked+label%3A%22%F0%9F%93%9A+Leadership%22"
          class="as-link"
        >
          people
        </a>
        who build it.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
